* Week 1 Codaisseur *

This repository contains my exercises from week 1 of the Codaisseur program.
I keep this repository around as a reference of what I learned during my 2 months training.

Contents

Day 2 - Basic Ruby programming - datatypes, methods, conditional statements.

Day 3 - Basic Ruby programming - loops, iterators

Day 4 - Object oriented programming - classes, instances

Day 5 - An intro to the web & Sinatra - A simple CRUD contact manager app using Sinatra

Day 6 - Ruby on Rails - My first RoR app -- pokemonshow! Another CRUD app but this time using RoR.

